*trojita-0.5 (04 Mar 2015)

  04 Mar 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> +trojita-0.5.ebuild,
  trojita-9999.ebuild:
  Version bump wrt bug #541286.

  29 Jan 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> trojita-9999.ebuild:
  Add Qt 5 support by Andreas Sturmlechner <andreas.sturmlechner@gmail.com> wrt
  bug #533600.

  14 Jun 2014; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> trojita-0.4.1.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #508776

  23 May 2014; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> trojita-0.4.1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #508776

  29 Apr 2014; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  trojita-9999.ebuild:
  Rename USE flag crypt to password requested by upstream maintainer Jan Kundrát
  <jkt@gentoo.org>.

  29 Apr 2014; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  trojita-9999.ebuild:
  Add USE flag crypt which enables optional support for secure password storage
  via dev-libs/qtkeychain by Jan Kundrát <jkt@gentoo.org>, bug #508774.

  21 Mar 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> -trojita-0.4.ebuild:
  Remove old

